en out of all the cities of Judah they came to seek the LORD."},{"id":"recTw9MblcYzFEZdT","ref":"2Chr.20.5","text":"And Jehoshaphat stood in the congregation of Judah and Jerusalem, in the house of the LORD, before the new court,"},{"id":"recmT760k8du4ljFj","ref":"2Chr.20.6","text":"And said, O LORD God of our fathers, art not thou God in heaven? and rulest not thou over all the kingdoms of the heathen? and in thine hand is there not power and might, so that none is able to withstand thee?"},{"id":"rectJE8wzErZUiGI9","ref":"2Chr.20.7","text":"Art not thou our God, who didst drive out the inhabitants of this land before thy people Israel, and gavest it to the seed of Abraham thy friend for ever?"},{"id":"recv1GhBRuRdODNvq","ref":"2Chr.20.8","text":"And they dwelt therein, and have built thee a sanctuary therein for thy name, saying,"}]}
